{'book': {'publisher': 'Continuum', 'synopsis': "First published in 1962 and long unavailable, BEYOND THE CHAINS OF ILLUSION is, only at first glance, a book about Marx and Freud--those two intellectual giants of the 20th century. Fromm here shows himself an outstanding interpreter of Marx. In all, Fromm's re-creation of the Freudian and Marxist way of thinking is, essentially, a look at the individual and society. BEYOND THE CHAINS OF ILLUSION will introduce many of today's readers to unknown aspects of Marx and Freud, as it also serves as a unique introduction to the life and mind of Erich Fromm as well. A new foreword by Fromm Literary Executor Rainer Funk puts this book into historic context and high relief.", 'language': 'en', 'image': 'https://images.isbndb.com/covers/89/75/9780826418975.jpg', 'title_long': 'Beyond the Chains of Illusion: My Encounter with Marx and Freud (Continuum Impacts, 55)', 'edition': 'New Ed', 'dimensions': 'Height: 7.81 Inches, Length: 5.06 Inches, Weight: 0.38801358112 Pounds, Width: 0.33 Inches', 'dimensions_structured': {'length': {'unit': 'inches', 'value': 5.06}, 'width': {'unit': 'inches', 'value': 0.33}, 'weight': {'unit': 'pounds', 'value': 0.38801358112}, 'height': {'unit': 'inches', 'value': 7.81}}, 'pages': 152, 'date_published': '2006-10-17', 'subjects': ['Health, Fitness & Dieting', 'Psychology & Counseling', 'Psychoanalysis', 'Medical Books', 'Psychology', 'General', 'Politics & Social Sciences', 'Philosophy', 'Modern', 'Politics & Government', 'Ideologies & Doctrines'], 'authors': ['Erich Fromm'], 'title': 'Beyond the Chains of Illusion: My Encounter with Marx and Freud (Continuum Impacts, 55)', 'isbn13': '9780826418975', 'msrp': 18.95, 'binding': 'Paperback', 'isbn': '082641897X', 'isbn10': '082641897X'}}